content:
Not sure if this is a completely stupid idea, so please tell me if it is.

Should we clean up (remove) the tags pre-rustup distribution of Clippy and with that remove the documentation of those versions from gh-pages? This would remove all those v0.0.212 to v0.0.51 tags and would remove almost as much directories from the gh-pages branch.

What do you think?
On the gh-pages branch in the respective directories.
I'm also in favor of it! :+1:
